    3rd/EmmyLuaCodeStyle/LuaParser/src/Parse/Mark.cpp
build $obj/code_format/TextRange.obj: cxx_code_format $
    3rd/EmmyLuaCodeStyle/LuaParser/src/Types/TextRange.cpp
